data.name: FANet
data.description: FANet: A Feedback Attention Network for Improved Biomedical Image Segmentation [IEEE Transactions on Neural Networks and Learning Systems]

evidence: Title and description present FANet as a specific model implementation: "FANet: A Feedback Attention Network for Improved Biomedical Image Segmentation" and "We propose a novel architecture called feedback attention network (FANet)..." indicating an end-user research application for segmentation.

Abstract describes using the network to produce segmentation results on datasets: "We show that our proposed feedback attention model provides a substantial improvement on most segmentation metrics tested on seven publicly available biomedical imaging datasets" indicating direct production of research results.
README provides only paper link, architecture figure, datasets, and citation, with no mention of package managers or binaries, implying use via cloning the repository/source.
